These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, dancer
1. the doctor is in an even position##4
2. the dancer is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | hiking | board-games |
| Job     | dancer    | doctor   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | water | milk        |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, punk
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, spanish
1. the chinese is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | gospel |
| Nationality   | chinese | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: garlic, avocado
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person eating avocado is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | soy-milk |
| Food       | garlic | avocado    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
