There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, australian
1. the brazilian is in an even position##4
2. the security-guard is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Job           | police-officer | security-guard |
| Nationality   | australian    | brazilian         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, golf
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, train
1. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | golf | rowing  |
| Transport   | train  | skateboard |

 #################################

 
